gemfire::HashSetOfCacheableKey

gemfire::HashSetOfCacheableKey Class Reference

Inherits gemfire::HashSetT< TKEY >< gemfire::SharedPtr >, and gemfire::SharedBase.

Detailed Description

A hash set of CacheableKey objects that also extends SharedBase for smart pointers.
